{"tid":1487062,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"仲記唔記得手足俾人斬！825一齊行出嚟！","createTime":"2019-08-19T06:02:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T11:25:41.000Z","uid":266916,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"67a752167d3aecd09a15de58eb55d6e16ecf3617","tid":1487062,"uid":266916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T06:02:37.000Z","msg":"舉行日期：2019年8月25日<br />\n時間：1500（集會）1530（遊行隊伍出發）<br />\n起點：葵涌運動場<br />\n終點：荃灣公園<br />\n<br />\n具體計劃之遊行路線將於稍後以圖像形式向各位發放<br />\n<br />\n聚焦目標：<br />\n1. 五大訴求　缺一不可<br />\n2. 要求全面追究參與警黑合作、發動及參與元朗及荃灣恐怖襲擊之恐怖份子的所有刑事責任<br />\n3. 要求全面追究涉事插贓嫁禍、妨礙司法公正之警員責任<br />\n4. 抗議警察偽裝示威者，及其發動的一切暴力行為<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QFWdEQj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQFWdEQj.jpg&h=06ada3de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KVfudak.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKVfudak.jpg&h=a4df2a31&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pwuyEQn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpwuyEQn.jpg&h=990bcc8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6rNMfoJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6rNMfoJ.jpg&h=fff2a674&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"35cc3b67b314bd266e8ba3494c20d388ab9b7de2","tid":1487062,"uid":281926,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T06:03:05.000Z","msg":"各位巴打絲打，頂住呀！<br />\n路還很長，記住齊上齊落！<br />\n<br />\n香港人可攻可守！智勇雙全！<br />\n記住<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>永不分化！不割蓆！不篤灰！</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>It&rsquo;s now or never</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qaQFjHY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqaQFjHY.jpg&h=817efdb4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1hvFjHY.jpg\" data